---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About Us | Shivay Construction Company"
  description="Learn about Shivay Construction Company, a registered Class-A railway contractor delivering OHE electrification, track works, and civil structures."
>
  <!-- About Hero -->
  <section class="about-hero-section section">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <span class="hero-badge">Who We Are</span>
      <h1>Our Foundation & Mission</h1>
      <p style="margin: 1.5rem auto 0; max-width: 75ch;">
        Shivay Construction Company was founded with a singular vision: to build reliable, high-performance transit infrastructure. Today, we stand as one of the trusted Class-A EPC contractors for Indian Railways, executing high-value e-tenders on time and with absolute precision.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Overview -->
  <section class="company-overview section section-alt">
    <div class="container grid-2">
      <div class="overview-text">
        <h2 class="heading-accent">Over a Decade of Engineering Excellence</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Headquartered in Noida, Uttar Pradesh, Shivay Construction Company operates primarily in critical railway sectors. Our capabilities range from initial earthworks and track linking to complex overhead line electrification (OHE) and interlocking signaling.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Through strategic bidding and collaborative joint ventures, we participate regularly in e-tenders published on the Indian Railways e-Procurement System (IREPS), delivering projects across multiple railway zones including NCR, WCR, ECoR, and SER.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our team comprises seasoned railway engineers, site managers, safety officers, and technical operators who understand the complexities of executing heavy civil infrastructure without disrupting existing train timetables.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="overview-values">
        <div class="card value-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <span class="value-num">01</span>
            <h3>Precision Engineering</h3>
            <p>Every sleeper laid, and every OHE wire tensioned, meets exact RDSO specifications with micro-level accuracy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card value-card mt-4">
          <div class="card-content">
            <span class="value-num">02</span>
            <h3>Timely Executions</h3>
            <p>We respect the strict railway block schedules. Our teams are trained to execute under tight traffic block windows without delays.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Safety & Quality Section -->
  <section class="safety-section section">
    <div class="container grid-2">
      <div class="safety-visual">
        <div class="safety-shield">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="80" height="80" fill="none" stroke="var(--accent)" stroke-width="1.5">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
            <polyline points="9 11 11 13 15 9" stroke-width="2" />
          </svg>
          <span class="safety-title">SAFETY FIRST</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="safety-text">
        <h2 class="heading-accent">Uncompromising Quality & Safety Standards</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Railway construction demands zero room for error. Shivay Construction Company operates under a strict **Zero-Accident Policy**. We conduct continuous safety drills for our OHE wiring crew and track alignment workers.
        </p>
        <div class="policies-box">
          <div class="policy-card">
            <h4>Quality Policy (ISO 9001:2015)</h4>
            <p>All materials—from steel structures and catenary wires to concrete sleepers and ballast—are sourced from RDSO-approved vendors and undergo strict testing in our lab prior to installation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="policy-card mt-4">
            <h4>Safety & Training Compliance</h4>
            <p>Our workforce is fully equipped with safety gear (Class-3 high-visibility jackets, insulated boots, and fall protection harnesses) and trained in Indian Railways safety protocols and rules.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Equipment & Fleet -->
  <section class="fleet-section section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="heading-accent-center mb-8">
        <h2>Machinery & Infrastructure Fleet</h2>
        <p class="text-center">Our robust inventory of specialized construction equipment allows us to execute projects self-sufficiently.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card fleet-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="fleet-icon">
              <!-- Utility/wiring truck icon placeholder -->
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="30" height="30" fill="none" stroke="var(--amber)" stroke-width="2">
                <rect x="2" y="11" width="13" height="8" rx="2" />
                <rect x="15" y="14" width="7" height="5" rx="1" />
                <circle cx="5" cy="19" r="2" />
                <circle cx="18" cy="19" r="2" />
                <path d="M7 11V7h5M12 4l3 3-3 3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>OHE Wiring & Utility Vehicles</h3>
            <p>Specialized wiring platforms and ladders for swift installation of catenary and contact wires during traffic blocks.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card fleet-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="fleet-icon">
              <!-- Excavator / earthmoving icon -->
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="30" height="30" fill="none" stroke="var(--amber)" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M2 20h20M4 20v-5h3v5M10 15h4v5h-4zM16 11l4 2v7" />
                <path d="M7 15l4-7h5l3 3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Heavy Earthmovers & Rollers</h3>
            <p>High-capacity hydraulic excavators, motor graders, and vibratory soil compactors for railway formation and blanketing.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card fleet-card">
          <div class="card-content">
            <div class="fleet-icon">
              <!-- Laser / alignment instruments -->
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="30" height="30" fill="none" stroke="var(--amber)" stroke-width="2">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" />
                <path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Alignment & Testing Systems</h3>
            <p>Advanced laser alignment tools, concrete strength testing equipment, and OHE tension measurement instrumentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero-section {
    padding-top: calc(var(--header-height) + 3rem);
    background: radial-gradient(circle at bottom, rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.03) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .company-overview {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
  }

  .overview-values {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .value-card {
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .value-num {
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.15);
    position: absolute;
    top: 1rem;
    right: 1.5rem;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* Safety Section CSS Graphic */
  .safety-visual {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .safety-shield {
    border: 2px dashed rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.2);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    width: 250px;
    background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.2);
  }

  .safety-title {
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .policies-box {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .policy-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .policy-card h4 {
    color: var(--amber);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .policy-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  /* Fleet styles */
  .fleet-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-dark);
  }

  .fleet-icon {
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.15);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .fleet-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .fleet-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .company-overview, .safety-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
